500
00:45:14,033 --> 00:45:15,498
You're what?

501
00:45:16,833 --> 00:45:17,924
Are you sure?

502
00:45:18,000 --> 00:45:21,364
Don't look so surprised. It's yours.

503
00:45:27,200 --> 00:45:28,927
When did it happen?

504
00:45:29,367 --> 00:45:32,162
Stourley, how could
you not have noticed?

505
00:45:34,866 --> 00:45:37,059
Must have been on the train to Rome.

506
00:45:37,367 --> 00:45:40,162
- But that was two months ago.
- Closer to three.

507
00:45:41,532 --> 00:45:43,589
You've hardly been near me since.

508
00:45:44,166 --> 00:45:48,064
Boullée and your stomachaches
are more important.

509
00:45:49,532 --> 00:45:52,987
- Are you sure this time?
- Yes.

510
00:45:57,833 --> 00:46:00,458
- Which side of the border?
- What?

511
00:46:05,633 --> 00:46:09,429
I think it was the Italian side...

512
00:46:09,532 --> 00:46:13,192
but I'm not exactly sure
how fast the train was going.

513
00:46:36,766 --> 00:46:39,664
<i>Wednesday, August 7.</i>
<i>Dear Étienne-Louis...</i>

514
00:46:39,733 --> 00:46:42,063
<i>apparently I'm to be a father.</i>

515
00:46:42,532 --> 00:46:44,158
<i>Were you ever a father?</i>

516
00:46:49,866 --> 00:46:54,423
<i>If your wife is unfaithful, how</i>
<i>can you ever be sure that</i>
<i>the child is really yours?</i>

517
00:46:55,333 --> 00:46:56,923
<i>My belly aches again.</i>

518
00:46:57,499 --> 00:46:59,658
<i>I eat only fruit, given up meat.</i>

519
00:47:02,966 --> 00:47:04,227
<i>Is that wise?</i>

520
00:47:08,566 --> 00:47:10,964
<i>With regards, Stourley Kracklite.</i>

521
00:47:13,766 --> 00:47:17,528
You think he's here for the architecture
or for the religion?

522
00:47:19,000 --> 00:47:20,727
What does his wife think?

523
00:47:21,766 --> 00:47:23,232
She does not think.

524
00:47:24,000 --> 00:47:25,296
She's American.

525
00:47:49,733 --> 00:47:51,222
He's learning.

526
00:49:45,033 --> 00:49:47,464
There you are. 20 million <i>lire.</i>

527
00:49:48,532 --> 00:49:52,226
Officially, it's been credited
to catering expenses. Bank it.

528
00:49:52,833 --> 00:49:55,697
We'll be able to make another
deposit in one month.

529
00:49:55,833 --> 00:49:57,526
Kracklite will never know.

530
00:49:57,799 --> 00:49:59,924
Boullée will be doing us a service.

531
00:50:00,000 --> 00:50:02,727
