532
00:50:03,133 --> 00:50:05,099
Very <i>Signor</i> Kracklite.

533
00:50:06,300 --> 00:50:08,027
It's even got his paunch.

534
00:50:08,566 --> 00:50:12,021
I'm sure you can sell it to him
as a fair likeness of his hero.

535
00:50:12,133 --> 00:50:15,565
And now, I have my assignation...

536
00:50:15,633 --> 00:50:17,361
