How do you know that?

567
00:52:31,799 --> 00:52:34,788
Don't be stupid. We are joking.

568
00:52:37,233 --> 00:52:39,096
- I'll give you a lift.
- Okay.

569
00:52:54,100 --> 00:52:55,531
<i>- Ciao.</i>
<i>- Ciao.</i>

570
00:52:58,066 --> 00:52:59,998
