650
01:04:44,966 --> 01:04:47,454
On account of the indigestible
consecrated host?

651
01:04:47,532 --> 01:04:49,498
No. Much simpler.

652
01:04:50,066 --> 01:04:53,123
"The Lord moves in mysterious ways...

653
01:04:53,400 --> 01:04:55,127
his duties to perform."

654
01:04:57,532 --> 01:05:00,521
I think you look beautiful pregnant.

655
01:05:00,666 --> 01:05:02,529
Like I said you would.

656
01:05:03,432 --> 01:05:06,660
- My sister wants to photograph you.
- What for?

657
01:05:08,100 --> 01:05:10,531
For her, for you...

658
01:05:11,466 --> 01:05:12,659
for me.

659
01:05:13,166 --> 01:05:14,825
And for Kracklite?

660
01:05:16,066 --> 01:05:17,293
Perhaps.

661
01:05:18,000 --> 01:05:20,431
- Would you like to do it?
- No.

662
01:05:21,300 --> 01:05:22,560
Why not?

663
01:05:22,766 --> 01:05:24,698
Your sister worries me.

664
01:05:25,066 --> 01:05:28,055
She's even more predatory than you are.

665
01:05:29,333 --> 01:05:30,321
Really?

666
01:05:30,400 --> 01:05:32,558
I think she's a hermaphrodite.

667
01:05:33,933 --> 01:05:36,365
I can assure you that she is not.

668
01:05:36,666 --> 01:05:38,292
How do you know?

669
01:05:38,966 --> 01:05:40,591
She is my sister.

670
01:05:41,233 --> 01:05:43,960
We used to bathe together.

671
01:05:44,066 --> 01:05:46,032
That was a long time ago.

672
01:05:47,033 --> 01:05:50,465
Is last Tuesday a long time ago?

673
01:05:52,000 --> 01:05:53,159
What?

674
01:05:54,766 --> 01:05:56,232
I was joking.

675
01:06:00,966 --> 01:06:02,227
Eighteen.

676
01:06:04,799 --> 01:06:06,163
Twenty-one.

677
01:06:07,333 --> 01:06:08,764
Twenty-four.

678
01:06:09,599 --> 01:06:10,895
Twenty-seven.

679
01:06:11,766 --> 01:06:13,096
Thirty.

680
01:06:19,233 --> 01:06:22,756
<i>Friday, January 10.</i>
<i>Dear Étienne-Louis...</i>

681
01:06:24,566 --> 01:06:26,362
<i>I don't like doctors.</i>

682
01:06:26,633 --> 01:06:29,259
<i>They always see you at a disadvantage.</i>

683
01:06:29,833 --> 01:06:32,197
<i>When they've studied
your private parts...</i>

684
01:06:32,267 --> 01:06:35,233
<i>smelled your breath,
fingered your tongue...</i>

685
01:06:35,666 --> 01:06:38,394
<i>how can you talk with them as an equal?</i>

686
01:06:42,300 --> 01:06:43,765
Are you ready?

687
01:06:51,267 --> 01:06:54,926
Now, <i>Signor</i> Kracklite,
would you lie on your left side, please?

688
01:06:55,000 --> 01:06:56,761
And bend your knees.

689
01:06:58,200 --> 01:07:00,791
I trust you know what we intend doing?

690
01:07:01,200 --> 01:07:02,995
It will be a little uncomfortable...

691
01:07:03,066 --> 01:07:06,362
but with the anesthetic,
you will feel very little.

692
01:07:07,267 --> 01:07:10,358
We intend examining your
intestine with a probe.

693
01:07:17,666 --> 01:07:19,064
With an optical light source...

694
01:07:19,133 --> 01:07:22,530
