into your large intestine...

695
01:07:22,599 --> 01:07:25,895
take live pictures that will appear
on a television monitor.

696
01:07:25,966 --> 01:07:29,262
This will allow us to search
for any irregularities.

697
01:07:30,733 --> 01:07:34,426
We will then make our full report
and ask you to come back.

698
01:07:53,499 --> 01:07:56,829
I wish I could take Kracklite's baby out...

699
01:07:57,699 --> 01:07:59,528
and put mine in its place.

700
01:08:03,066 --> 01:08:05,429
What difference would that make?

701
01:08:06,400 --> 01:08:09,332
It would still be the child of an architect.

702
01:08:10,100 --> 01:08:13,554
Yes, but at least with me,
it would not be posthumously.

703
01:08:14,000 --> 01:08:15,261
Meaning?

704
01:08:17,400 --> 01:08:21,422
The way Kracklite is going,
he won't last till summer.

705
01:08:36,799 --> 01:08:40,993
Tell me, Kracklite,
why don't you photograph women?

706
01:08:41,566 --> 01:08:44,362
Different metabolism, different organs...

707
01:08:44,566 --> 01:08:46,396
different complaints.

708
01:08:50,367 --> 01:08:52,196
Have you eaten?

709
01:08:55,233 --> 01:08:57,460
Well, if you buy me a meal...

710
01:08:57,633 --> 01:08:59,861
I'll take the photos for you.

711
01:09:06,633 --> 01:09:09,599
